        <div id="tool-sound" class="tool-panel" style="display:none">
          <div class="sound-monitor-container">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:20px; color:var(--primary)">馃攰 鐝骇澹拌礉绠＄悊</h3>
            <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:20px;">瀹炴椂鐩戞祴鐝骇澹伴煶鍒嗚礉锛屽府鍔╃淮鎸佽鍫傜З搴忋€傜偣鍑汇€屽紑濮嬬洃鍚€嶅惎鐢ㄩ害鍏嬮銆?/p>

            <!-- 鎺у埗闈㈡澘 -->
            <div class="sound-control-panel">
              <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btnStartSoundMonitor">馃帳 寮€濮嬬洃鍚?/button>
              <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btnStopSoundMonitor" style="display:none;">鈴癸笍 鍋滄鐩戝惉</button>
              <div class="sound-threshold-control">
                <label>璀︽姤闃堝€?</label>
