        <div id="tool-memo" class="tool-panel" style="display:none">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:20px; color:var(--primary)">馃摑 鐝骇澶囧繕褰?/h3>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:20px;">璁剧疆鐝骇鎻愰啋銆佸ぇ浜嬩欢锛岀鐞嗘椂闂存棩鏈燂紝鎺ユ敹浜嬩欢鎻愰啋銆?/p>
          
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 15px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef); border-radius: var(--radius);">
